ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000Ctc8z:ref

Around the next time of sync is when they repopulate. We have some as old as this one here:
[cid:image001.png@01DAD2C3.D6797270]

The sync is set to be every 15 minutes with Azure Active Directory. While we may have SOME devices that haven't been properly removed, most are not in Azure AD but are still re-appearing within Endpoint. This one for example is showing in Endpoint:
[cid:image003.png@01DAD2C4.5FC65F70]


But when checking Azure, it's no longer present.

[cid:image004.png@01DAD2C4.5FC65F70]
